      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically sound, this unit has had the 'Big Three' addressed: the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled, rod bearings replaced with treated shells, and the rear subframe reinforced to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. While the finish shows minor road-going patina, the suspension geometry remains true and the powertrain delivers the visceral, high-strung performance expected of an M-division legend.",
